@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8001
@threadId = demo-thread-001

### 流式聊天
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "我有鸡蛋、番茄和土豆，推荐一道适合新手的晚饭",
  "thread_id": "{{threadId}}"
}

### 查看历史消息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/messages?thread_id={{threadId}}

### 清空历史消息
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/messages?thread_id={{threadId}}

### 获取图片上传地址，需要先配置 OSS 环境变量
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/oss/presign?filename=test.png
